{"tid":2490392,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人一轉天氣加埋戴口罩搞到爛面","createTime":"2021-04-15T14:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T06:10:22.000Z","uid":25953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a9bcb605dd509736c2add577c8d7229b21b46187","tid":2490392,"uid":25953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:21:45.000Z","msg":"話說上年4月開始我兩邊面開始起粒粒又紅色一撻撻<br />\n去睇醫生醫生話係戴口罩係社會嘅錯<br />\n食咗3個月抗生素係咁搽藥膏都唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後我都唔記得佢7月個陣咩事自己好返啲<br />\n而嚟到今年...<br />\n我又開始爛面啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又痕又核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全唔想出街食飯 一除口罩實嚇死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問有冇巴絲都有呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想嚟圍爐取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0852e53e1ae2fdfd234c7edb29a210d6c57cb92","tid":2490392,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:23:05.000Z","msg":"人生太短出手要更大"},{"pid":"d5038e7f7aa290b71608192e6c5bd67acce2ea3c","tid":2490392,"uid":25953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:37:11.000Z","msg":"有圖慎入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"807270754b6a3b5519dc03eab8b30f48d7c5e0b2","tid":2490392,"uid":14261,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d5038e7f7aa290b71608192e6c5bd67acce2ea3c","tid":2490392,"uid":25953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:37:11.000Z","msg":"有圖慎入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T15:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3fcf6a988c4b43ef50b2d03f6e72ed0907e6ac9","tid":2490392,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T15:44:56.000Z","msg":"似係D油脂粒加敏感<br />\n朝早搽D防敏感潤膚膏先戴口罩<br />\n口罩一日上下午換一個<br />\n唔好再用D咩洗面奶化妝品落妝水"},{"pid":"7677ccd89ce94edb85944128f140c558c582aebe","tid":2490392,"uid":60825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:46:17.000Z","msg":"暗粒嚟 同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n爆到一發不可收拾<br />\n4月頭頂唔順去咗做機<br />\n朝早 夜晚敷保濕mask<br />\n一日換2 3個口罩<br />\n呢兩日終於好好多 起碼冇再生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前冇試過咁 爛面好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1015eca42d10268002ee55789c3ac5b54d4f2ac3","tid":2490392,"uid":25953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"807270754b6a3b5519dc03eab8b30f48d7c5e0b2","tid":2490392,"uid":14261,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d5038e7f7aa290b71608192e6c5bd67acce2ea3c","tid":2490392,"uid":25953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:37:11.000Z","msg":"有圖慎入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T15:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T23:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e3161cc7bccc3dbda596fba842e61d157ce031","tid":2490392,"uid":25953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q